{"tid":217574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【女神去英國】日本最美公主佳子 將赴英當交換學生","createTime":"2017-04-26T01:19:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T18:07:56.000Z","uid":73262,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"639f53ef380a316d7c3c3c0c7da9fe2a5fff7070","tid":217574,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T01:19:47.000Z","msg":"日本宅男女神、秋篠宮文仁親王次女佳子公主，今年9月會前往英國利茲大學（University of Leeds）短期留學，至明年6月結束才回國。<br />\n<br />\n22歲的佳子公主現時是國際基督教大學的三年級生，宮內廳周一宣佈，佳子公主今次是透過交換生計劃前往利茲大學留學，而在當地取得的學分，經審查後亦可轉為國際基督教大學的學分。<br />\n<br />\n宮內廳指，佳子公主一直有意出國留學，她與國際基督教大學教職員商議後，決定選擇收容不少來自各國的留學生、具有高度多樣性與國際性，而且可選修課程領域廣泛的利茲大學。去年10月佳子公主報名參加交換生計劃，今年3月收到利茲大學的取錄通知。<br />\n<br />\n日本《朝日新聞》<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56611686&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170426\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56611686%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170426&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhatgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=decfdaa2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56611686%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170426&h=dbb0da56\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56611686&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170426</a>"},{"pid":"a484a12885bd7ef111bef404c0eec73f2f23a3f8","tid":217574,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T01:21:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/7mgqcn98\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F7mgqcn98&h=98589c21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港d有錢佬會唔會即刻派晒d仔去搞入學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07d1adaff9ce88f31e0a4fc62052a7204b83bfa9","tid":217574,"uid":56467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T01:29:11.000Z","msg":"冇喇冇喇 連公主都要去做洋腸既性奴<img src=